<section class="tension" id="how-it-works">
<div class="section-inner">
<div class="section-eyebrow">The problem</div>
<h2>Many job evaluation systems were built for a different world.</h2>
<div class="tension-grid">
<div class="tension-left">
<p>A world of fixed roles and stable structures isn't how modern organisations operate. Roles evolve, structures shift, and governance expectations keep rising.</p>
<p>Engage was built for the way organisations work now — structured methodology with practical usability, so you grade roles with more confidence and less friction.</p>
</div>
<div class="tension-right">
<div class="pain-label">Many job evaluation systems are still:</div>
<ul class="eng-still">
<li><span class="chip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg></span>Slow to implement and difficult to explain</li>
<li><span class="chip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 2h8l4 4v16H6z"/><path d="M14 2v4h4"/><path d="M9 12h6"/><path d="M9 16h6"/></svg></span>Dependent on outdated job descriptions</li>
<li><span class="chip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 15.5-6.2L21 8"/><path d="M21 3v5h-5"/><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-15.5 6.2L3 16"/><path d="M3 21v-5h5"/></svg></span>Hard to maintain as roles evolve</li>
<li><span class="chip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2 12s3.5-6.5 10-6.5c2 0 3.7.6 5.1 1.4"/><path d="M22 12s-3.5 6.5-10 6.5c-2 0-3.7-.6-5.1-1.4"/><path d="M4 4l16 16"/></svg></span>Opaque — a black box that erodes trust</li>
<li><span class="chip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v10"/><path d="M14.6 9.4A2.6 2 0 0 0 12 8c-1.4 0-2.5.8-2.5 1.9 0 2.6 5 1.3 5 3.9 0 1.1-1.1 1.9-2.5 1.9a2.6 2 0 0 1-2.6-1.4"/></svg></span>Highly reliant on expensive external consultants</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
