<div class="diff-card"><span class="diff-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2 12s3.5-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3.5 7-10 7-10-7-10-7z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></span><h3>Transparent</h3><p>Clear logic. No mystery scoring. No black box. Decisions you can explain and defend.</p></div>
